Package: screen-share-tab
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Little Place Labs <hello@littleplacelabs.com>
Depends: ffmpeg, python3 (>= 3.9), python3-venv, curl
Recommends: xdotool, vainfo
Description: Stream laptop screens to a tablet browser over WiFi
 Stream your laptop display and external monitor to any browser on your
 local network. Supports hardware-accelerated encoding (NVENC/VAAPI),
 quality and FPS controls, cursor highlighting, pinch-to-zoom, keyboard
 shortcuts, mDNS discovery, and auto-reconnect.
 .
 Run 'screen-share-tab' in any terminal, then open the URL on your tablet.
